Hello World :-)

eclipse install new Software Arduino

Datei package_esp32_index.json in ~./arduinocdt kopieren
Arduino package esp32 (Espressif Systems) installieren
Arduino lib LoRa installieren
Arduino lib Display installieren

https://exploreembedded.com/wiki/Setting_up_Eclipse_for_ESP-IDF

/.arduinocdt/packages/esp32/hardware/esp32/1.0.0/platform.txt:
runtime.tools.xtensa-esp32-elf-gcc.path = ~/.arduinocdt/packages/esp32/tools/xtensa-esp32-elf
runtime.tools.esptool.path = ~/.arduinocdt/packages/esp32/tools/esptool

#runtime.tools.xtensa-esp32-elf-gcc.path = "{runtime.platform.path}/../../../tools/xtensa-esp32-elf"
#runtime.tools.esptool.path = "{runtime.platform.path}/../../../tools/esptool"

tools.esptool.path=~/.arduinocdt/packages/esp32/tools/esptool

#tools.esptool.path={runtime.tools.esptool.path}

Toolchain
https://dl.espressif.com/dl/xtensa-esp32-elf-linux64-1.22.0-80-g6c4433a-5.2.0.tar.gz
nach ~/.arduinocdt/packages/esp32/tools

sudo apt-get install python-serial

sudo adduser user dialout (enable tty for user)

